            <title>[LUCENE-2640] add LuceneTestCase[J4].newField</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LUCENE-2640</link>
                <project id="12310110" key="LUCENE">Lucene - Core</project>
                        <description>&lt;p&gt;I think it would be good to vary the different field options in tests.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;For example, we do this with IW settings (newIndexWriterConfig), and directories (newDirectory).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This patch adds newField(), it works just like new Field(), except it will sometimes turns on extra options:&lt;br/&gt;
Stored fields, term vectors, additional term vectors data, etc.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
